{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1131,"text":"My first love was for the night sky."},{"time":4432,"text":"Love is complicated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5998,"text":"You're looking at a fly-through of the \nHubble Space Telescope Ultra-Deep Field,"},{"time":10527,"text":"one of the most distant images\nof our universe ever observed."},{"time":14639,"text":"Everything you see here is a galaxy,"},{"time":17153,"text":"comprised of billions of stars each."},{"time":20160,"text":"And the farthest galaxy is \na trillion, trillion kilometers away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25881,"text":"As an astrophysicist, I have\nthe awesome privilege of studying"},{"time":28805,"text":"some of the most exotic objects \nin our universe."},{"time":32252,"text":"The objects that have captivated me \nfrom first crush throughout my career"},{"time":36064,"text":"are supermassive, \nhyperactive black holes."},{"time":41813,"text":"Weighing one to 10 billion times \nthe mass of our own sun,"},{"time":45931,"text":"these galactic black holes \nare devouring material,"},{"time":48825,"text":"at a rate of upwards of \n1,000 times more"},{"time":52145,"text":"than your \"average\" \nsupermassive black hole."},{"time":55512,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57640,"text":"These two characteristics,"},{"time":59334,"text":"with a few others, make them quasars."},{"time":62548,"text":"At the same time, the objects I study"},{"time":65465,"text":"are producing some of the most\npowerful particle streams"},{"time":68242,"text":"ever observed."},{"time":69937,"text":"These narrow streams, called jets,"},{"time":72777,"text":"are moving at 99.99 percent \nof the speed of light,"},{"time":77385,"text":"and are pointed directly at the Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81368,"text":"These jetted, Earth-pointed, hyperactive\nand supermassive black holes"},{"time":87257,"text":"are called blazars, or blazing quasars."},{"time":91801,"text":"What makes blazars so special\nis that they're some of the universe's"},{"time":95282,"text":"most efficient particle accelerators,"},{"time":97802,"text":"transporting incredible amounts\nof energy throughout a galaxy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102720,"text":"Here, I'm showing an\nartist's conception of a blazar."},{"time":105469,"text":"The dinner plate by which \nmaterial falls onto the black hole"},{"time":108669,"text":"is called the accretion disc,"},{"time":110256,"text":"shown here in blue."},{"time":112082,"text":"Some of that material is slingshotted\naround the black hole"},{"time":115061,"text":"and accelerated to insanely high speeds\n"},{"time":117085,"text":"in the jet, shown here in white."},{"time":119912,"text":"Although the blazar system is rare,"},{"time":122599,"text":"the process by which nature\npulls in material via a disk,"},{"time":125606,"text":"and then flings some of it out via a jet,\nis more common."},{"time":129647,"text":"We'll eventually zoom out of \nthe blazar system"},{"time":132091,"text":"to show its approximate relationship\nto the larger galactic context."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141890,"text":"Beyond the cosmic accounting\nof what goes in to what goes out,"},{"time":146295,"text":"one of the hot topics in \nblazar astrophysics right now"},{"time":149342,"text":"is where the highest-energy \njet emission comes from."},{"time":153053,"text":"In this image, I'm interested\nin where this white blob forms"},{"time":156974,"text":"and if, as a result, there's any \nrelationship between the jet"},{"time":160617,"text":"and the accretion disc material."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163483,"text":"Clear answers to this question"},{"time":165286,"text":"were almost completely\ninaccessible until 2008,"},{"time":168401,"text":"when NASA launched a new telescope\nthat better detects gamma ray light --"},{"time":172675,"text":"that is, light with energies\na million times higher"},{"time":175387,"text":"than your standard x-ray scan."},{"time":178934,"text":"I simultaneously compare variations\nbetween the gamma ray light data"},{"time":182824,"text":"and the visible light data from\nday to day and year to year,"},{"time":186493,"text":"to better localize these gamma ray blobs."},{"time":189767,"text":"My research shows that in some instances,"},{"time":192453,"text":"these blobs form much closer\nto the black hole"},{"time":195513,"text":"than we initially thought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197873,"text":"As we more confidently localize"},{"time":199764,"text":"where these gamma ray \nblobs are forming,"},{"time":202060,"text":"we can better understand how jets\nare being accelerated,"},{"time":205583,"text":"and ultimately reveal \nthe dynamic processes"},{"time":208191,"text":"by which some of the most fascinating\nobjects in our universe are formed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213892,"text":"This all started as a love story."},{"time":217501,"text":"And it still is."},{"time":219414,"text":"This love transformed me from \na curious, stargazing young girl"},{"time":223624,"text":"to a professional astrophysicist,"},{"time":225445,"text":"hot on the heels of celestial discovery."},{"time":228782,"text":"Who knew that chasing after the universe"},{"time":231202,"text":"would ground me so deeply\nto my mission here on Earth."},{"time":235000,"text":"Then again, when do we ever know\nwhere love's first flutter"},{"time":238468,"text":"will truly take us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239942,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241171,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}